snippet.title: PIOZILA 2 : ANIMAL ADVENTURES (GOOGLE PLAY / APP STORE)
snippet.description:
Help cute animals collect all the stars.

Guide animals through unique and colorful levels and chapters to collect stars.
Unlock additional animals using collected stars.
Control the animal by touching your screen or rotating your device.

Available for free on google play and app store.

google play - https://apps.apple.com/us/app/piozila-2/id6450461710
app store - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.menamenagames.piozila2

https://menamenagames.com
